alerts_data.title: Declining Footfall Trend
alerts_data.message: Multiple facilities showing declining patient footfall in recent months
alerts_data.action: Immediate review of resource allocation and community outreach programs

alerts_data.title: Low Industrial Outreach Performance
alerts_data.message: Below target e-pehchaan card adoption and ESI Mitra identification
alerts_data.action: Enhance industrial engagement and digital adoption programs

alerts_data.title: Outstanding Performance Growth
alerts_data.message: Exceptional performance improvement and efficiency gains
alerts_data.action: Document best practices and implement network-wide

alerts_data.title: High Referral Dependency
alerts_data.message: Some facilities showing above-average referral rates
alerts_data.action: Strengthen specialist services and diagnostic capabilities

components: Patient Footfall Utilization (40% weightage) - Measures patient access and facility utilization
Prescription Fulfillment Efficiency (50% weightage) - Evaluates service delivery effectiveness
Service Diversity and Certificate Processing (10% weightage) - Assesses comprehensive care provision
calculation_details: Prescription Efficiency: (Total Prescriptions / Total Footfall) × 10, maximum 10 points
efficiency_methodology.trend_analysis: Percentage changes calculated month-over-month for Weekly and Monthly time periods
